<br>
Sanctus Seru - Most people have heard of this city, it's the &quot;bad good&quot; city... if that makes any sense. Evils are KOS here, which I assume means DEs (I saw a DE corpse, after all), trolls, ogres, and iksar. Everyone else cons either indifferent to apprehensive with most of the people in the city (Hand of Seru guardsmen, most merchants, etc.), and apparently dubious to a variety of other factions. Hunting in Mons Letalis, though difficult, supposedly can give you LOTS of Seru faction without hurting Katta Castellum or other factions.<br>
<br>
And boy, do you ever wanna do that! SS is a really slick place, wide open, with a roman feel to it, TONS of shops (probably too many; I saw some redundant ones), several banks, an arena right out of Gladiator (complete with a crowd and &quot;crowd noise&quot;) - you can even buy an &quot;arena ticket&quot; from the arena master, I assume enabling a scripted event where you duel an NPC in the arena - all under blue skies. A nice, pretty little town, even if it is a police state... <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><CENTER><IMG SRC="http://members.aol.com/uryvichk/mbanner.jpg"></CENTER></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ushikariiapoccalypse.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shikarii Apoccalypse</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Steel Warrior Contributor</span><br>  Posts: 772<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/19/01 10:29:18 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: A Brief Note on Luclin Factions</span><hr size=1> sanctus seru is a cool city. <br>
