<br>
Most of the quests in Shar Vahl are either Vah Shir only, or give no faction. HOWEVER, you can get faction in Shadeweaver's Thicket by killing Loda Kai bandits and the like. You can't miss them; they're humans. They're in league with one of the two alien baby races (well that's what they look like!), but NOT the Shak Dratha (the other one... name is eluding me, they're brownish), and killing them lowers both of those and raises Shar Vahl guard faction. There are a few other newbie quests but I didn't have the patience to find all the items on newbie mob corpses to gauge what factions they provide. You should be indifferent anyway... also note that killing one alien baby race raises your faction with the other... my assumption is that if you kill the Loda Kai and their alien allies long enough, the Shak Dratha will actually like you. Not that it would do you much good, but there you go. Grimlings may also give faction, in Hollowshade Moor; I haven't spied on their main camp in the southeast islands to find out. More to come! <p><CENTER><IMG SRC="http://members.aol.com/uryvichk/mbanner.jpg"></CENTER></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showMessage?topicID=207.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showMessage?topicID=233.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=241.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.threadControl?topicID=241.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a>